This is a special update, app gets totally upgraded and optimized, plus the following NEW FEATURES:

● New Photo Collage & Layout tool, most easy-to-use, have your photo collage done by very few taps, support modifying the collage layout manually as well.
● New Text Adding tool, include a lot of Free Fancy Fonts.
● Support full-size photo edit, keep high resolution when saving and sharing.
